<c.ms Gothic>兄さんやろ</c.ms Gothic>

163
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:55,910
<c.ms Gothic>だって… 会社を起こそうと</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>動き始めたのは お前だろ</c.ms Gothic>

164
00:08:56,619 --> 00:08:58,996
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）あいつは俺を立てるんだ</c.ms Gothic>

165
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,958
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）あの人らしいです</c.ms Gothic>

166
00:09:02,041 --> 00:09:02,917
<c.ms Gothic>（フッと笑う声）</c.ms Gothic>

167
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:08,256
<c.ms Gothic>10年ほどで会社も上場して</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>うまく回っていた</c.ms Gothic>

168
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:10,550
<c.ms Gothic>だけど ふと気づくと</c.ms Gothic>

169
00:09:12,301 --> 00:09:14,554
<c.ms Gothic>社員はみんな 泰三を見ているんだ</c.ms Gothic>

170
00:09:18,474 --> 00:09:20,393
<c.ms Gothic>ある時から</c.ms Gothic>

171
00:09:20,476 --> 00:09:23,229
<c.ms Gothic>それが恐怖に感じるように</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>なってきた</c.ms Gothic>

172
00:09:26,148 --> 00:09:28,109
<c.ms Gothic>ビットバレーの社長って</c.ms Gothic>

173
00:09:28,192 --> 00:09:31,362
<c.ms Gothic>絶対 泰三さんがやった方が</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>いいと思うんですよね</c.ms Gothic>

174
00:09:31,445 --> 00:09:33,447
<c.ms Gothic>うん 沢辺社長もいいけど</c.ms Gothic>

175
00:09:33,531 --> 00:09:35,032
<c.ms Gothic>そんなこと言うな</c.ms Gothic>

176
00:09:38,119 --> 00:09:42,456
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）もし あいつが本気で</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>この会社を乗っ取ろうとしたら</c.ms Gothic>

177
00:09:44,667 --> 00:09:48,504
<c.ms Gothic>俺の味方につく奴なんて</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>いないんじゃないかって</c.ms Gothic>

178
00:09:49,255 --> 00:09:50,715
<c.ms Gothic>どんどん怖くなってきてな</c.ms Gothic>

179
00:09:53,884 --> 00:09:55,678
<c.ms Gothic>泰三を追い出すことに決めた</c.ms Gothic>

180
00:09:55,761 --> 00:09:57,638
<c.ms Gothic>（音楽が止まる）</c.ms Gothic>

181
00:09:57,722 --> 00:09:59,974
<c.ms Gothic>セクハラ事件をでっちあげた</c.ms Gothic>

182
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:03,060
<c.ms Gothic>どないしたん？</c.ms Gothic>

183
00:10:03,144 --> 00:10:06,355
<c.ms Gothic>そんな真面目な顔して</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>話があるって</c.ms Gothic>

184
00:10:06,439 --> 00:10:07,398
<c.ms Gothic>（若き沢辺の小さなため息）</c.ms Gothic>

185
00:10:07,481 --> 00:10:08,482
<c.ms Gothic>泰三…</c.ms Gothic>

186
00:10:09,942 --> 00:10:12,570
<c.ms Gothic>飲み会があると</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>女性社員の</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>本田</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(ほんだ)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>さん</c.ms Gothic>

187
00:10:12,653 --> 00:10:14,697
<c.ms Gothic>（若き沢辺）送って帰ってるよね</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>（若き泰三）うん</c.ms Gothic>

188
00:10:15,281 --> 00:10:17,533
<c.ms Gothic>本田さんがタクシー乗って</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>うちに帰ったら</c.ms Gothic>

189
00:10:18,784 --> 00:10:19,994
<c.ms Gothic>泰三が無理矢理ついてきて</c.ms Gothic>

190
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:23,664
<c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>強姦</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(ごうかん)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>に近いようなことされたって</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>泣きながら言ってた</c.ms Gothic>

191
00:10:26,792 --> 00:10:27,918
<c.ms Gothic>ホンマに…</c.ms Gothic>

192
00:10:29,253 --> 00:10:30,838
<c.ms Gothic>本田さんが言うてきたんやな？</c.ms Gothic>

193
00:10:31,547 --> 00:10:34,717
<c.ms Gothic>（不穏な音楽）</c.ms Gothic>

194
00:10:36,385 --> 00:10:37,345
<c.ms Gothic>そうだよ</c.ms Gothic>

195
00:10:38,054 --> 00:10:40,640
<c.ms Gothic>これが表沙汰になったら事件になる</c.ms Gothic>

196
00:10:45,144 --> 00:10:46,145
<c.ms Gothic>そうやな</c.ms Gothic>

197
00:10:52,943 --> 00:10:55,112
<c.ms Gothic>（立ち上がる音）</c.ms Gothic>

198
00:10:56,947 --> 00:10:58,491
<c.ms Gothic>責任を取って</c.ms Gothic>

199
00:11:00,076 --> 00:11:01,494
<c.ms Gothic>俺は会社を辞める</c.ms Gothic>

200
00:11:02,828 --> 00:11:03,913
<c.ms Gothic>色々…</c.ms Gothic>

201
00:11:04,747 --> 00:11:06,540
<c.ms Gothic>騒がして すみませんでした</c.ms Gothic>

202
00:11:08,376 --> 00:11:09,585
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）そう言った</c.ms Gothic>

203
00:11:11,837 --> 00:11:14,006
<c.ms Gothic>何も言い訳しないどころか</c.ms Gothic>

204
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:15,383
<c.ms Gothic>頭を下げた</c.ms Gothic>

205
00:11:17,301 --> 00:11:18,469
<c.ms Gothic>何もしていないのに</c.ms Gothic>

206
00:11:18,552 --> 00:11:19,720
<c.ms Gothic>（ドアが閉まる音）</c.ms Gothic>

207
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:24,725
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）なぜ言い訳もしなかったか</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>わかるか？</c.ms Gothic>

208
00:11:27,687 --> 00:11:29,063
<c.ms Gothic>気づいたんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

209
00:11:29,855 --> 00:11:31,232
<c.ms Gothic>俺の気持ちを全部</c.ms Gothic>

210
00:11:32,858 --> 00:11:34,985
<c.ms Gothic>泰三に嫉妬してる想いを</c.ms Gothic>

211
00:11:37,321 --> 00:11:38,364
<c.ms Gothic>沢辺さんは</c.ms Gothic>

212
00:11:39,407 --> 00:11:41,909
<c.ms Gothic>その時のこと 後悔してますか？</c.ms Gothic>

213
00:11:43,744 --> 00:11:45,079
<c.ms Gothic>悪いとは思ってる</c.ms Gothic>

214
00:11:47,123 --> 00:11:48,332
<c.ms Gothic>だけど後悔はしない</c.ms Gothic>

215
00:11:50,292 --> 00:11:51,877
<c.ms Gothic>じゃないと今がないから</c.ms Gothic>

216
00:11:56,298 --> 00:11:58,968
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）リーダーは</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>会社に二人もいらない</c.ms Gothic>

217
00:12:02,096 --> 00:12:03,264
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）えっ…</c.ms Gothic>

218
00:12:03,347 --> 00:12:05,599
<c.ms Gothic>（深く息を吸う音）</c.ms Gothic>

219
00:12:05,683 --> 00:12:06,642
<c.ms Gothic>なんで…</c.ms Gothic>

220
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:10,563
<c.ms Gothic>どうして…</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>その話を僕に？</c.ms Gothic>

221
00:12:10,646 --> 00:12:12,189
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺）君は…</c.ms Gothic>

222
00:12:12,273 --> 00:12:15,067
<c.ms Gothic>あの時の俺と同じ気持ちに</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>なるはずだ</c.ms Gothic>

223
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:19,321
<c.ms Gothic>そんなことはないです</c.ms Gothic>

224
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,742
<c.ms Gothic>あいつは社長ですから</c.ms Gothic>

225
00:12:23,743 --> 00:12:24,577
<c.ms Gothic>火高君</c.ms Gothic>

226
00:12:27,997 --> 00:12:30,583
<c.ms Gothic>鉄平君と君は いずれ</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>袂</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(たもと)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>を分かつ</c.ms Gothic>

227
00:12:33,377 --> 00:12:36,714
<c.ms Gothic>絶対に… そんなことはないです</c.ms Gothic>

228
00:12:39,383 --> 00:12:40,384
<c.ms Gothic>そうだね</c.ms Gothic>

229
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,681
<c.ms Gothic>（沢辺のため息）</c.ms Gothic>

230
00:12:49,769 --> 00:12:51,520
<c.ms Gothic>華子さん 聞いてください</c.ms Gothic>

231
00:12:51,604 --> 00:12:53,022
<c.ms Gothic>昨日の私の動画</c.ms Gothic>

232
00:12:53,105 --> 00:12:54,899
<c.ms Gothic>１日で１万再生なんです</c.ms Gothic>

233
00:12:54,982 --> 00:12:56,776
<c.ms Gothic>（一同 口々に）ええっ！</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>すごい</c.ms Gothic>

234
00:12:56,859 --> 00:12:57,860
<c.ms Gothic>（ざわめく声）</c.ms Gothic>

235
00:12:57,943 --> 00:12:59,528
<c.ms Gothic>コメント かなり来てて</c.ms Gothic>

236
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:00,446
<c.ms Gothic>（女性たちのざわめき）</c.ms Gothic>

237
00:13:00,529 --> 00:13:02,531
<c.ms Gothic>正直 モデルやってる時より</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>楽しいです</c.ms Gothic>

238
00:13:02,615 --> 00:13:03,449
<c.ms Gothic>（一斉に笑う声）</c.ms Gothic>

239
00:13:03,532 --> 00:13:05,743
<c.ms Gothic>（口々に）わかるわー</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>すごいわかる</c.ms Gothic>

240
00:13:11,290 --> 00:13:13,334
<c.ms Gothic>（近づいてくる足音）</c.ms Gothic>

241
00:13:13,417 --> 00:13:14,418
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）大丈夫？</c.ms Gothic>

242
00:13:15,461 --> 00:13:16,462
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）あっ…</c.ms Gothic>

243
00:13:16,545 --> 00:13:17,463
<c.ms Gothic>大丈夫</c.ms Gothic>

244
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:19,590
<c.ms Gothic>すぐ戻ります</c.ms Gothic>

245
00:13:22,593 --> 00:13:24,512
<c.ms Gothic>ツイッター 見たよ</c.ms Gothic>

246
00:13:26,222 --> 00:13:27,681
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）“どうすれば</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>いいんだろ”</c.ms Gothic>

247
00:13:27,765 --> 00:13:29,141
<c.ms Gothic>“どうしようも</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>ないのかな”</c.ms Gothic>

248
00:13:29,225 --> 00:13:30,893
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）ああ</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>そんな所に</c.ms Gothic>

249
00:13:30,976 --> 00:13:32,603
<c.ms Gothic>書いちゃダメだよね</c.ms Gothic>

250
00:13:32,686 --> 00:13:33,687
<c.ms Gothic>いいんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

251
00:13:36,649 --> 00:13:38,609
<c.ms Gothic>本当に</c.ms Gothic>

252
00:13:38,692 --> 00:13:41,278
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業部</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>売ることになったら</c.ms Gothic>

253
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:45,491
<c.ms Gothic>みんなに どうやって</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>説明しようかなって</c.ms Gothic>

254
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:49,078
<c.ms Gothic>なんか裏切られた気持ちになって</c.ms Gothic>

255
00:13:49,161 --> 00:13:51,372
<c.ms Gothic>辞めちゃうんじゃないかなって</c.ms Gothic>

256
00:13:51,455 --> 00:13:53,915
<c.ms Gothic>そういう子も出てくるだろうね</c.ms Gothic>

257
00:13:54,583 --> 00:13:55,709
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）私も…</c.ms Gothic>

258
00:13:56,544 --> 00:13:58,254
<c.ms Gothic>自信ないな</c.ms Gothic>

259
00:13:59,171 --> 00:14:01,257
<c.ms Gothic>別の会社行って働くって</c.ms Gothic>

260
00:14:02,716 --> 00:14:04,969
<c.ms Gothic>みんなと一緒だからやれたのに</c.ms Gothic>

261
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:07,596
<c.ms Gothic>俺 今回ばかりは</c.ms Gothic>

262
00:14:08,597 --> 00:14:10,558
<c.ms Gothic>あいつが間違ってると思う</c.ms Gothic>

263
00:14:16,605 --> 00:14:18,315
<c.ms Gothic>火高さんにとって</c.ms Gothic>

264
00:14:19,191 --> 00:14:21,318
<c.ms Gothic>社長は どんな存在？</c.ms Gothic>

265
00:14:22,069 --> 00:14:25,573
<c.ms Gothic>だって二人は同じ歳だけど</c.ms Gothic>

266
00:14:25,656 --> 00:14:27,825
<c.ms Gothic>鉄平さんが社長で</c.ms Gothic>

267
00:14:27,908 --> 00:14:29,326
<c.ms Gothic>火高さんは</c.ms Gothic>

268
00:14:30,077 --> 00:14:31,954
<c.ms Gothic>大変なことも多い</c.ms Gothic>

269
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:35,958
<c.ms Gothic>俺はさ</c.ms Gothic>

270
00:14:36,792 --> 00:14:39,461
<c.ms Gothic>福井県から出てきて</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>東京の大学に入ったんだよね</c.ms Gothic>

271
00:14:39,962 --> 00:14:41,171
<c.ms Gothic>で 大学の時に</c.ms Gothic>

272
00:14:41,255 --> 00:14:43,549
<c.ms Gothic>友達に誘われてイベントに行ったら</c.ms Gothic>

273
00:14:43,632 --> 00:14:46,093
<c.ms Gothic>それが鉄平のイベントだった</c.ms Gothic>

274
00:14:46,176 --> 00:14:47,428
<c.ms Gothic>私も行ったやつだ</c.ms Gothic>

275
00:14:48,512 --> 00:14:49,638
<c.ms Gothic>目の前でさ</c.ms Gothic>

276
00:14:51,056 --> 00:14:52,349
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）同い歳で</c.ms Gothic>

277
00:14:52,933 --> 00:14:55,769
<c.ms Gothic>大学生なのに社長になってる</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>ヤツがいてさ</c.ms Gothic>

278
00:14:56,270 --> 00:15:00,024
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）シャンパン一気して</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>伝説作ろうぜって</c.ms Gothic>

279
00:15:00,107 --> 00:15:01,567
<c.ms Gothic>そいつが</c.ms Gothic>

280
00:15:01,650 --> 00:15:04,904
<c.ms Gothic>ビットバレーエージェントに</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>入ったら 隣の席にいてさ</c.ms Gothic>

281
00:15:04,987 --> 00:15:06,322
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）そしたら</c.ms Gothic>

282
00:15:06,405 --> 00:15:10,075
<c.ms Gothic>１年ちょっとで あいつが</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>会社を辞めることになって</c.ms Gothic>

283
00:15:10,159 --> 00:15:12,077
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）火高さんも一緒に</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>辞めることになった</c.ms Gothic>

284
00:15:14,663 --> 00:15:16,999
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）会社で叫んでる</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>あいつの背中を見た時に</c.ms Gothic>

285
00:15:18,792 --> 00:15:22,212
<c.ms Gothic>こいつの背中を見て</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>生きていこうって</c.ms Gothic>

286
00:15:22,296 --> 00:15:23,797
<c.ms Gothic>思ったんだよね</c.ms Gothic>

287
00:15:27,468 --> 00:15:29,678
<c.ms Gothic>でも 今は違う</c.ms Gothic>

288
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:34,350
<c.ms Gothic>今の鉄平は なんか… 違う</c.ms Gothic>

289
00:15:38,228 --> 00:15:40,147
<c.ms Gothic>大丈夫だよ</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>俺が止めるから</c.ms Gothic>

290
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:43,359
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業部は</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>売らない</c.ms Gothic>

291
00:15:56,872 --> 00:15:57,790
<c.ms Gothic>（</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>翔太</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(しょうた)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>）社長</c.ms Gothic>

292
00:15:58,457 --> 00:16:00,751
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業部の件は</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>どうなったんですか</c.ms Gothic>

293
00:16:02,878 --> 00:16:05,130
<c.ms Gothic>（鉄平）ああ…</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）ああ じゃないですよ</c.ms Gothic>

294
00:16:05,756 --> 00:16:07,466
<c.ms Gothic>あのこと やっぱり僕は…</c.ms Gothic>

295
00:16:09,134 --> 00:16:10,636
<c.ms Gothic>この後 会議をする</c.ms Gothic>

296
00:16:11,595 --> 00:16:13,097
<c.ms Gothic>そこで みんなで決めるんだ</c.ms Gothic>

297
00:16:39,665 --> 00:16:42,126
<c.ms Gothic>何の会議をするんですか</c.ms Gothic>

298
00:16:46,714 --> 00:16:47,715
<c.ms Gothic>ちょっと待って</c.ms Gothic>

299
00:16:48,632 --> 00:16:50,009
<c.ms Gothic>見てもらいたいものがある</c.ms Gothic>

300
00:16:50,884 --> 00:16:53,095
<c.ms Gothic>ビットラブのデモ映像</c.ms Gothic>

301
00:16:53,178 --> 00:16:54,596
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）今 見なくても</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>いいんじゃないかな</c.ms Gothic>

302
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:57,349
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）今は それよりも</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>大事な話があるだろ？</c.ms Gothic>

303
00:16:59,184 --> 00:17:01,270
<c.ms Gothic>こっちだって大事な話だ</c.ms Gothic>

304
00:17:01,353 --> 00:17:02,896
<c.ms Gothic>会社の未来だぞ</c.ms Gothic>

305
00:17:05,023 --> 00:17:06,066
<c.ms Gothic>とりあえず見よう</c.ms Gothic>

306
00:17:07,483 --> 00:17:08,444
<c.ms Gothic>どうぞ</c.ms Gothic>

307
00:17:10,194 --> 00:17:11,238
<c.ms Gothic>（明るい音楽）</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>“仮想恋愛サービス</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>ビットラブ”</c.ms Gothic>

308
00:17:11,238 --> 00:17:11,280
<c.ms Gothic>“仮想恋愛サービス</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>ビットラブ”</c.ms Gothic>

309
00:17:12,823 --> 00:17:13,741
<c.ms Gothic>（</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>堀田</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(ほりた)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>）まず</c.ms Gothic>

310
00:17:14,366 --> 00:17:17,661
<c.ms Gothic>ネット上で お互いを指名して</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>そうしたら…</c.ms Gothic>

311
00:17:19,747 --> 00:17:22,332
<c.ms Gothic>ネット上の街で</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>デートができる</c.ms Gothic>

312
00:17:24,334 --> 00:17:25,461
<c.ms Gothic>（堀田）たとえば</c.ms Gothic>

313
00:17:25,544 --> 00:17:27,296
<c.ms Gothic>映画館をクリックすると</c.ms Gothic>

314
00:17:30,215 --> 00:17:32,843
<c.ms Gothic>一緒に映画が見れて</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>会話もできる</c.ms Gothic>

315
00:17:34,595 --> 00:17:37,264
<c.ms Gothic>そして手を</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>クリックすると</c.ms Gothic>

316
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:41,852
<c.ms Gothic>仮想だとしても</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>かなりドキドキできるはずです</c.ms Gothic>

317
00:17:44,021 --> 00:17:45,314
<c.ms Gothic>そして こんなことも…</c.ms Gothic>

318
00:17:46,565 --> 00:17:48,734
<c.ms Gothic>ホテルをクリックして</c.ms Gothic>

319
00:17:48,817 --> 00:17:50,736
<c.ms Gothic>ホテルに入って</c.ms Gothic>

320
00:17:54,364 --> 00:17:56,033
<c.ms Gothic>こんなことまで</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>できてしまう</c.ms Gothic>

321
00:17:56,909 --> 00:17:58,202
<c.ms Gothic>家にいるのに</c.ms Gothic>

322
00:17:58,285 --> 00:18:00,662
<c.ms Gothic>一緒にデートしてるような</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>気分になる</c.ms Gothic>

323
00:18:01,205 --> 00:18:02,122
<c.ms Gothic>まさに</c.ms Gothic>

324
00:18:02,998 --> 00:18:05,250
<c.ms Gothic>仮想恋愛 ビットラブ</c.ms Gothic>

325
00:18:07,044 --> 00:18:09,046
<c.ms Gothic>これを見て確信に変わった</c.ms Gothic>

326
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:12,633
<c.ms Gothic>これは時代の波に乗る</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>どころじゃない</c.ms Gothic>

327
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:15,135
<c.ms Gothic>時代を変えれる</c.ms Gothic>

328
00:18:15,219 --> 00:18:17,346
<c.ms Gothic>俺達で時代を作ることができる</c.ms Gothic>

329
00:18:17,930 --> 00:18:19,932
<c.ms Gothic>（堀田）だね！</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>だけど</c.ms Gothic>

330
00:18:20,015 --> 00:18:22,392
<c.ms Gothic>これを完ぺきに製作するとなると</c.ms Gothic>

331
00:18:23,811 --> 00:18:25,229
<c.ms Gothic>かなり お金がかかる</c.ms Gothic>

332
00:18:31,735 --> 00:18:33,445
<c.ms Gothic>この新規事業のために</c.ms Gothic>

333
00:18:34,363 --> 00:18:37,032
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業を</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>売却するかどうか</c.ms Gothic>

334
00:18:37,574 --> 00:18:39,493
<c.ms Gothic>話し合って答えって出るんですかね</c.ms Gothic>

335
00:18:39,576 --> 00:18:40,702
<c.ms Gothic>多数決をとる</c.ms Gothic>

336
00:18:43,831 --> 00:18:45,624
<c.ms Gothic>多数決で… 決めんの？</c.ms Gothic>

337
00:18:51,713 --> 00:18:52,589
<c.ms Gothic>まず…</c.ms Gothic>

338
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:56,385
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業売却に</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>賛成の人</c.ms Gothic>

339
00:18:57,344 --> 00:18:58,428
<c.ms Gothic>手を挙げてくれ</c.ms Gothic>

340
00:19:02,975 --> 00:19:04,309
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）一人ですよ</c.ms Gothic>

341
00:19:04,393 --> 00:19:06,061
<c.ms Gothic>こうなること わかってたでしょ</c.ms Gothic>

342
00:19:06,145 --> 00:19:08,105
<c.ms Gothic>あ 俺も賛成</c.ms Gothic>

343
00:19:09,273 --> 00:19:11,441
<c.ms Gothic>堀田さんは本当にいいんですか？</c.ms Gothic>

344
00:19:11,525 --> 00:19:12,776
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）売っちゃっても</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>（堀田）俺は</c.ms Gothic>

345
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:15,612
<c.ms Gothic>エンジニアとして</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>このビットラブを作りたいんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

346
00:19:15,696 --> 00:19:17,489
<c.ms Gothic>華子さんたち いなくなるんすよ</c.ms Gothic>

347
00:19:17,573 --> 00:19:19,658
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）頑張ってくれてんのに</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>（堀田）俺は！</c.ms Gothic>

348
00:19:19,741 --> 00:19:22,244
<c.ms Gothic>俺にしかできない仕事がしたいの</c.ms Gothic>

349
00:19:22,327 --> 00:19:23,745
<c.ms Gothic>それが俺の生きる意味</c.ms Gothic>

350
00:19:27,249 --> 00:19:28,292
<c.ms Gothic>じゃあ 次は…</c.ms Gothic>

351
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:29,710
<c.ms Gothic>いや もう結果わかってるでしょ</c.ms Gothic>

352
00:19:29,793 --> 00:19:31,378
<c.ms Gothic>じゃなくても やるんだ</c.ms Gothic>

353
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:35,340
<c.ms Gothic>インフルエンサー事業売却に</c.ms Gothic>

354
00:19:36,008 --> 00:19:37,050
<c.ms Gothic>反対の人</c.ms Gothic>

355
00:19:37,593 --> 00:19:38,510
<c.ms Gothic>手を挙げてくれ</c.ms Gothic>

356
00:19:45,267 --> 00:19:47,102
<c.ms Gothic>（火高）３対２</c.ms Gothic>

357
00:19:47,895 --> 00:19:48,729
<c.ms Gothic>決まりだね</c.ms Gothic>

358
00:19:48,812 --> 00:19:51,106
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）こうなること</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>わかってましたよね？</c.ms Gothic>

359
00:19:54,067 --> 00:19:55,110
<c.ms Gothic>どうした 華子？</c.ms Gothic>

360
00:19:55,194 --> 00:19:57,237
<c.ms Gothic>（翔太）どうもこうもないでしょ</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>しっかり手を挙げてる</c.ms Gothic>

361
00:19:57,321 --> 00:19:58,238
<c.ms Gothic>（鉄平）だまれ 翔太</c.ms Gothic>

362
00:20:00,866 --> 00:20:01,992
<c.ms Gothic>（華子の震える息づかい）</c.ms Gothic>

363
00:20:15,005 --> 00:20:16,256
<c.ms Gothic>ごめんなさい</c.ms Gothic>

364
00:20:21,136 --> 00:20:22,346
<c.ms Gothic>私は…</c.ms Gothic>

365
00:20:31,813 --> 00:20:33,065
<c.ms Gothic>賛成で</c.ms Gothic>

366
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:41,949
<c.ms Gothic>100％は賛成じゃないんだけど</c.ms Gothic>

367
00:20:43,075 --> 00:20:44,326
<c.ms Gothic>でも…</c.ms Gothic>

368
00:20:45,619 --> 00:20:46,662
<c.ms Gothic>さっき</c.ms Gothic>

369
00:20:49,623 --> 00:20:51,208
<c.ms Gothic>堀田さんが言った言葉</c.ms Gothic>

370
00:20:54,169 --> 00:20:55,254
<c.ms Gothic>“俺は…”</c.ms Gothic>

371
00:20:56,797 --> 00:20:59,091
<c.ms Gothic>“俺にしかできない仕事をしたい”</c.ms Gothic>

372
00:20:59,967 --> 00:21:01,510
<c.ms Gothic>“それが生きてる意味”</c.ms Gothic>

373
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:11,728
<c.ms Gothic>私は…</c.ms Gothic>

374
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:17,567
<c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>大分</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(おおいた)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>の田舎で育って…</c.ms Gothic>

375
00:21:18,443 --> 00:21:21,905
<c.ms Gothic>（静かな音楽）</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>（鳥のさえずり）</c.ms Gothic>

376
00:21:23,198 --> 00:21:25,701
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>矢沢永吉</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>(やざわえいきち)</c.ms Gothic></c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic> の</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>「成りあがり」読んで</c.ms Gothic>

377
00:21:26,785 --> 00:21:29,871
<c.ms Gothic>“この人 すっげぇー”って思って</c.ms Gothic>

378
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:33,333
<c.ms Gothic>絶対自分も何かやってやるって</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>思った</c.ms Gothic>

379
00:21:36,586 --> 00:21:39,256
<c.ms Gothic>東京出てきて 自分で売り込んだら</c.ms Gothic>

380
00:21:40,007 --> 00:21:42,634
<c.ms Gothic>たまたま読者モデルから始まって</c.ms Gothic>

381
00:21:42,718 --> 00:21:44,052
<c.ms Gothic>モデルになれてた</c.ms Gothic>

382
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:48,223
<c.ms Gothic>雑誌でモデルやってる時は</c.ms Gothic>

383
00:21:49,474 --> 00:21:52,227
<c.ms Gothic>正直 調子乗ってたかもしれない</c.ms Gothic>

384
00:21:54,271 --> 00:21:55,814
<c.ms Gothic>だけどさ</c.ms Gothic>

385
00:21:55,897 --> 00:21:59,818
<c.ms Gothic>雑誌の売り上げが落ち込んで</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>雑誌潰れて 仕事なくなって</c.ms Gothic>

386
00:22:00,610 --> 00:22:03,530
<c.ms Gothic>気づくと自分には何もなくなってた</c.ms Gothic>

387
00:22:04,114 --> 00:22:04,948
<c.ms Gothic>（無声）</c.ms Gothic>

388
00:22:05,032 --> 00:22:06,408
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）学歴もない</c.ms Gothic>

389
00:22:07,701 --> 00:22:08,702
<c.ms Gothic>資格もない</c.ms Gothic>

390
00:22:09,953 --> 00:22:11,288
<c.ms Gothic>サロン行ってもさ</c.ms Gothic>

391
00:22:11,913 --> 00:22:14,875
<c.ms Gothic>元モデルじゃ価値がないって</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>言われちゃった</c.ms Gothic>

392
00:22:14,958 --> 00:22:17,544
<c.ms Gothic>美人なんか沢山いるって言われた</c.ms Gothic>

393
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:21,631
<c.ms Gothic>だけどね</c.ms Gothic>

394
00:22:25,344 --> 00:22:26,303
<c.ms Gothic>社長と出会って</c.ms Gothic>

395
00:22:28,722 --> 00:22:31,808
<c.ms Gothic>こんな人いるんだって思った</c.ms Gothic>

396
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:34,019
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）落ちてるパスタ食べて</c.ms Gothic>

397
00:22:34,978 --> 00:22:37,147
<c.ms Gothic>人前に全裸になって</c.ms Gothic>

398
00:22:37,230 --> 00:22:40,650
<c.ms Gothic>21世紀を代表する会社を</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>作るんだって</c.ms Gothic>

399
00:22:40,734 --> 00:22:43,070
<c.ms Gothic>ギリギリですよ もうギリギリ</c.ms Gothic>

400
00:22:43,153 --> 00:22:45,489
<c.ms Gothic>イタい人とのギリギリのところ</c.ms Gothic>

401
00:22:46,448 --> 00:22:48,367
<c.ms Gothic>（しゃくりあげて）だけどね</c.ms Gothic>

402
00:22:50,577 --> 00:22:53,246
<c.ms Gothic>夢に ちょっとずつ近づいてってる</c.ms Gothic>

403
00:22:54,998 --> 00:22:56,166
<c.ms Gothic>ちょっとずつ</c.ms Gothic>

404
00:22:58,418 --> 00:22:59,920
<c.ms Gothic>私は今まで</c.ms Gothic>

405
00:23:04,091 --> 00:23:05,801
<c.ms Gothic>歳の近い人に</c.ms Gothic>

406
00:23:09,137 --> 00:23:10,806
<c.ms Gothic>悔しい思いや</c.ms Gothic>

407
00:23:13,308 --> 00:23:15,143
<c.ms Gothic>嫉妬を抱いたことはあった</c.ms Gothic>

408
00:23:18,271 --> 00:23:20,232
<c.ms Gothic>だけど生まれて初めて</c.ms Gothic>

409
00:23:25,028 --> 00:23:26,780
<c.ms Gothic>尊敬を抱いた</c.ms Gothic>

410
00:23:33,078 --> 00:23:34,246
<c.ms Gothic>鉄平さんは</c.ms Gothic>

411
00:23:37,999 --> 00:23:40,836
<c.ms Gothic>私が働いている会社の社長です</c.ms Gothic>

412
00:23:43,088 --> 00:23:44,840
<c.ms Gothic>尊敬してる社長が</c.ms Gothic>

413
00:23:48,218 --> 00:23:50,887
<c.ms Gothic>夢の扉を全力で開けてたら</c.ms Gothic>

414
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:57,227
<c.ms Gothic>私は手伝うべきなんです</c.ms Gothic>

415
00:23:59,438 --> 00:24:00,480
<c.ms Gothic>だから</c.ms Gothic>

416
00:24:04,443 --> 00:24:06,194
<c.ms Gothic>私が みんなをまとめます</c.ms Gothic>

417
00:24:20,625 --> 00:24:21,626
<c.ms Gothic>華子</c.ms Gothic>

418
00:24:24,629 --> 00:24:25,672
<c.ms Gothic>ありがとう</c.ms Gothic>

419
00:24:29,843 --> 00:24:30,927
<c.ms Gothic>やります</c.ms Gothic>

420
00:24:32,596 --> 00:24:33,513
<c.ms Gothic>（小さく笑う声）</c.ms Gothic>

421
00:24:49,905 --> 00:24:51,156
<c.ms Gothic>すみません</c.ms Gothic>

422
00:24:52,532 --> 00:24:53,533
<c.ms Gothic>俺は…</c.ms Gothic>

423
00:24:55,827 --> 00:24:58,246
<c.ms Gothic>華子のこと 尊敬するよ</c.ms Gothic>

424
00:25:03,543 --> 00:25:06,004
<c.ms Gothic>やめてください そういうの</c.ms Gothic>

425
00:25:13,386 --> 00:25:14,346
<c.ms Gothic>社長…</c.ms Gothic>

426
00:25:15,889 --> 00:25:17,974
<c.ms Gothic>１つ聞いてもいいですか</c.ms Gothic>

427
00:25:19,643 --> 00:25:20,644
<c.ms Gothic>なんだ</c.ms Gothic>

428
00:25:21,645 --> 00:25:23,021
<c.ms Gothic>もし</c.ms Gothic>

429
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:27,776
<c.ms Gothic>反対が多かったら</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>どうするつもりだったの？</c.ms Gothic>

430
00:25:30,862 --> 00:25:32,489
<c.ms Gothic>それでも実行した</c.ms Gothic>

431
00:25:35,659 --> 00:25:36,701
<c.ms Gothic>（鉄平）ただ…</c.ms Gothic>

432
00:25:39,329 --> 00:25:40,705
<c.ms Gothic>ただ何かが</c.ms Gothic>

433
00:25:41,498 --> 00:25:43,083
<c.ms Gothic>変わるんじゃないかって</c.ms Gothic>

434
00:25:44,751 --> 00:25:46,002
<c.ms Gothic>信じてた</c.ms Gothic>

435
00:25:46,086 --> 00:25:47,003
<c.ms Gothic>（華子がフッと笑う声）</c.ms Gothic>

436
00:25:49,297 --> 00:25:50,257
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）ほら</c.ms Gothic>

437
00:25:52,050 --> 00:25:53,093
<c.ms Gothic>やっぱり</c.ms Gothic>

438
00:25:54,302 --> 00:25:56,846
<c.ms Gothic>ちょっとずつ近づいてるんですよ</c.ms Gothic>

439
00:25:59,266 --> 00:26:00,433
<c.ms Gothic>成功に</c.ms Gothic>

440
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:07,857
<c.ms Gothic>俺は…</c.ms Gothic>

441
00:26:08,650 --> 00:26:10,360
<c.ms Gothic>（深く息を吸い込む音）</c.ms Gothic>

442
00:26:11,236 --> 00:26:14,614
<c.ms Gothic>絶対に21世紀を代表する</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>会社を作る</c.ms Gothic>

443
00:26:14,698 --> 00:26:17,450
<c.ms Gothic>（勢いのある音楽）</c.ms Gothic>

444
00:26:17,534 --> 00:26:18,827
<c.ms Gothic>（深く息を吸い込む音）</c.ms Gothic>

445
00:26:19,869 --> 00:26:21,037
<c.ms Gothic>だから みんな</c.ms Gothic>

446
00:26:26,918 --> 00:26:28,086
<c.ms Gothic>力を貸してくれ</c.ms Gothic>

447
00:26:31,089 --> 00:26:33,341
<c.ms Gothic>（音楽が盛り上がる）</c.ms Gothic>

448
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:46,688
<c.ms Gothic>（社員）ビットバレー</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>エージェントに</c.ms Gothic>

449
00:26:46,771 --> 00:26:48,523
<c.ms Gothic>買収ってどういうことですか</c.ms Gothic>

450
00:26:48,607 --> 00:26:50,650
<c.ms Gothic>それって私たち</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>売られるってことですか</c.ms Gothic>

451
00:26:50,734 --> 00:26:53,445
<c.ms Gothic>なんで 何の相談もなしに</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>売られなきゃいけないんですか</c.ms Gothic>

452
00:26:53,528 --> 00:26:54,446
<c.ms Gothic>みんな 安心して</c.ms Gothic>

453
00:26:54,529 --> 00:26:56,489
<c.ms Gothic>会社が移るだけで</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>何も変わらないから</c.ms Gothic>

454
00:26:56,573 --> 00:26:57,616
<c.ms Gothic>お金はどうなんですか</c.ms Gothic>

455
00:26:57,699 --> 00:26:58,783
<c.ms Gothic>変わらないよ</c.ms Gothic>

456
00:26:58,867 --> 00:27:00,660
<c.ms Gothic>私も一緒に行くから 安心して</c.ms Gothic>

457
00:27:00,744 --> 00:27:01,745
<c.ms Gothic>絶対 怪しいよね</c.ms Gothic>

458
00:27:01,828 --> 00:27:02,787
<c.ms Gothic>ギャラも安くされるよ</c.ms Gothic>

459
00:27:02,871 --> 00:27:04,956
<c.ms Gothic>そもそも相談もないって</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>どういうことですか？</c.ms Gothic>

460
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:06,750
<c.ms Gothic>（女子社員）ってか</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>道具じゃねえっつうの</c.ms Gothic>

461
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:08,627
<c.ms Gothic>やっぱり納得いかないです</c.ms Gothic>

462
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:11,254
<c.ms Gothic>これだったら辞めて</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>自分でやったほうがいいんですけど</c.ms Gothic>

463
00:27:11,338 --> 00:27:12,172
<c.ms Gothic>（女子社員２）おかしいと思います</c.ms Gothic>

464
00:27:12,255 --> 00:27:13,548
<c.ms Gothic>やってらんない</c.ms Gothic>

465
00:27:13,632 --> 00:27:16,801
<c.ms Gothic>（社員たちの不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

466
00:27:16,885 --> 00:27:18,637
<c.ms Gothic>（口々に不満を言う声）</c.ms Gothic>

467
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:21,348
<c.ms Gothic>（社員たちが詰め寄る声）</c.ms Gothic>

468
00:27:21,431 --> 00:27:23,141
<c.ms Gothic>（社員たちの不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

469
00:27:23,224 --> 00:27:25,518
<c.ms Gothic>（女子社員の不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

470
00:27:25,602 --> 00:27:28,104
<c.ms Gothic>（止まらない不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

471
00:27:28,188 --> 00:27:30,023
<c.ms Gothic>（社員たちの不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

472
00:27:30,106 --> 00:27:32,817
<c.ms Gothic>（高まる不満の声）</c.ms Gothic>

473
00:27:32,901 --> 00:27:35,195
<c.ms Gothic>（華子）うっせえな</c.ms Gothic>

474
00:27:35,278 --> 00:27:36,363
<c.ms Gothic>お前らな</c.ms Gothic>

475
00:27:38,823 --> 00:27:41,826
<c.ms Gothic>会社は学校じゃねぇんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

476
00:27:42,911 --> 00:27:44,537
<c.ms Gothic>（エキサイティングな音楽）</c.ms Gothic>

477
00:27:46,956 --> 00:27:48,708
<c.ms Gothic>騒いでんじゃねぇよ</c.ms Gothic>

478
00:27:49,459 --> 00:27:51,044
<c.ms Gothic>そもそも私らは</c.ms Gothic>

479
00:27:52,671 --> 00:27:54,798
<c.ms Gothic>クビになったモデルなんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

480
00:27:54,881 --> 00:27:56,800
<c.ms Gothic>いらないですって言われた</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>モデルなんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

481
00:27:57,926 --> 00:27:58,843
<c.ms Gothic>だけど</c.ms Gothic>

482
00:28:01,221 --> 00:28:03,348
<c.ms Gothic>今は働く場所があんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

483
00:28:04,557 --> 00:28:07,227
<c.ms Gothic>自分たちが自分たちらしく</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>いられる場所があるんだよ</c.ms Gothic>

484
00:28:12,691 --> 00:28:14,442
<c.ms Gothic>新しい場所でもさ</c.ms Gothic>

485
00:28:16,611 --> 00:28:19,656
<c.ms Gothic>うちらは うちらにしか</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>できないこと やっていこうよ</c.ms Gothic>

486
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:33,086
<c.ms Gothic>そうだよね</c.ms Gothic>

487
00:28:38,133 --> 00:28:39,092
